<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُولَاتِ}</span> ... ذَوَاتِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاتَمِرُوا}</span> ... وَلْيَامُرْ بَعْضُكُمْ بَعْضًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمَعْرُوفٍ}</span> ... بِمَا عُرِفَ مِنْ سَمَاحَةٍ، وَطِيبِ نَفْسٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَعَاسَرْتُمْ}</span> ... تَشَاحَحْتُمْ فِي الإِرْضَاعِ فَامْتَنَعَ الأَبُ مِنَ الأُجْرَةِ، وَالأُمُّ مِنَ الرَّضَاعِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُدِرَ}</span> ... ضُيِّقَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَكَأَيِّن}</span> ... كَثِيرٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَتَتْ}</span> ... عَصَتْ، وَتَجَبَّرَتْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُّكْرًا}</span> ... مُنْكَرًا عَظِيمًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
